Package scalf.cmsc335.finalProject.threaded Description

Contains all of the classes for objects that run in their own thread. The abstract classes and interfaces in this package exist to provide better communication between objects, as well as to reduce code duplication.
Author:
Samuel Scalf
Date:
10 OCT 2020
School:
University of Maryland Global Campus
Professor:
Dr. Osama A. Morad, Ph.D.
Course:
CMSC 335 6380 Object-Oriented and Concurrent Programming (2208)
